，端木正为了振兴师门，王恩珠为了再也不愚钝，每个人进入太乙山都有自己的学习目的，有着少年的好强与上进心。大家不打不相识，从彼此防范的陌生人，到共同学习的伙伴，面对各种突发事件，一起成长，在各自学习领域取得收获。";s:13:"vod_play_from";s:14:"kkyun$$$kkm3u8";s:15:"vod_play_server";s:7:"no$$$no";s:13:"vod_play_note";s:3:"$$$";s:12:"vod_play_url";s:5667:"第01集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/WyN9g1WEa6MEYXQZ#第02集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/GJAmG3J8qenWtso1#第03集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/A89JIKFZUJ7K7TUv#第04集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/nodN6SZDnM8iIBYP#第05集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/t5rib9XBP6vhp7QY#第06集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/Z0sTwQGebx1JxQzL#第07集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/E1F0Il2TLwP7YNjd#第08集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/WKC2TfV1yORnGVC2#第09集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/TrmdW92majrymEkL#第10集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/Lb0uMorIgP2NJVtt#第11集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/DdvpB8BTMmiagTmR#第12集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/ydWLOsHG1FazNtdY#第13集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/1rijSBHTYlji62rM#第14集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/wJOTlWvOI8lB3Lue#第15集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/HgIE7nWsVlwRHAhz#第16集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/t3CL1K4QDLFLEiyQ#第17集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/r617PxexWUF9Ll9j#第18集$https://vip888.kuyun99.com/share/fDx81DGxBhJTZbTL#第19集$https://vip888.kuyun99.com/share/DnmyRlLzZjzcG4Eq#第20集$https://vip888.kuyun99.com/share/N5LMGa2R7UZwvDFt#第21集$https://vip888.kuyun99.com/share/tfRGdOVtRwoy2bi5#第22集$https://vip888.kuyun99.com/share/YMAWVbTyB0RcDrLa#第23集$https://vip888.kuyun99.com/share/p01AZFDM3859olDr#第24集$https://vip888.kuyun99.com/share/TGNQS4ootBQWyOz8#第25集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/BycJecd8Kxxwr3zc#第26集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/S02prOMcoQ4lVrqU#第27集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/sqQzhbmMmW5jAQEY#第28集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/7qHSQuu3ToucM2b9#第29集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/myBCCgxYksNyLUyu#第30集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/WeHq30MB7hYkw1I6#第31集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/XCgkuehbCGulMN2t#第32集$https://vip.kuyun99.com/share/RRF5h76fikwv7uJ3#第33集$https://vip888.kuyun99.com/share/k3eB9lEOpFBFrlOb#第34集$https://v